    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>At method _formatName(...) of ClassZend_Controller_Dispatcher (subpackage: Dispatcher)
I found typing error at second statement of that method
original type :
- $unformatted = preg_replace('[^a-z0-9 ]', '', $unformatted); 
i suggest :
- $unformatted = preg_replace('/[^a-z0-9 ]/', '', $unformatted);</p>

<p>IMHO: this actually can remove any non alphanumeric characters</p>

